label: pistol
description: Ancient pattern automatic pistol. Weak and short range, but quick.

label: pump shotgun
description: Ancient design. Deadly, but short range.

label: survival rifle
description: Ancient bolt-action rifle. Good range, Good power, low rate of fire.

label: assault rifle
description: A general-purpose military weapon for field or urban combat. It fires a three-round burst. Good range, low power, high rate of fire.

label: sniper rifle
description: Ancient pattern military sniper rifle. Bolt action. Long range, great accuracy and power.

label: Machine pistol
description: A micro-submachine gun. Short range, low power, high rate of fire. Very quick to aim and fire.

label: heavy SMG
description: A compact, wide-caliber slug-thrower. Very short range, but it packs a punch and handles quite well.

label: minigun
description: A multi-barrel machine gun with an extremely high rate of fire. Mechanoid-built.

label: doomsday rocket launcher
description: A single-use rocket launcher for quick retribution.

label: triple rocket launcher
description: A single-use rocket launcher that fires 3 projectiles in quick succession.

label: heavy charge blaster
description: Charged-shot blaster for area suppressive fire. Mechanoid-built.

label: charge lance
description: Charged-shot rail-assisted lance weapon. Fires a single charged shot at high velocity.
